title: ‘The ones that bowed must pay’: Dems who voted to approve Trump cabinet nominees spark outrage
text:
‘The ones that bowed must pay’: Dems who voted to approve Trump cabinet nominees spark outrage Posted at 8:09 pm on January 31, 2017 by Brett T. 
The New York Times published a graphic Tuesday showing how senators had voted on President Donald Trump’s cabinet nominees, but plenty chose to interpret the image as a wanted poster instead. How each senator voted on President Trump’s cabinet nominees https://t.co/ILqP6HJ830 pic.twitter.com/BZnMEvjpMU 
— The New York Times (@nytimes) January 31, 2017 14 Senate Democrats have voted for every Trump nominee so far (5) pic.twitter.com/Pp5SpY72Fm
